{"tid":489064,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(異能+懸疑+小咸)推介一套叫做「欲鬼」既漫畫比大家","createTime":"2017-12-04T10:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T10:35:50.000Z","uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"59f7b687956317018ff95b0bac6b4b777682489b","tid":489064,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:13:00.000Z","msg":"故事圍繞住男主同埋女主阿哥<br />\n講人既慾望假如over某個地步就會變成欲鬼<br />\n而欲鬼同普通人分別在於有異能<br />\n男主係殺人欲 女主係被殺欲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女主阿哥全劇智慧擔當+極度極度悲慘既過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢套野好睇在打鬥場面同分析既篇幅平衡得好好 <br />\n有小小似東京食屍鬼既格局 <br />\n而故事一直係到走主線 所以唔會悶咁濟<br />\n最緊要係畫風好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/161845_614811c00fdbe6dd1499c50f683ed8f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F161845_614811c00fdbe6dd1499c50f683ed8f0.jpg&h=7b7f24b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/162650_d27b5de2c5309ec7ce6340b9713c5823.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F162650_d27b5de2c5309ec7ce6340b9713c5823.jpg&h=8ae822c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/162703_a41a021cb25f858739d30daaf795411c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F162703_a41a021cb25f858739d30daaf795411c.jpg&h=74eb1153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n絕配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/162502_78eda99a5c1189907e21ebffb69cf789.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F162502_78eda99a5c1189907e21ebffb69c